data.text: @donkristian76 LMAO, it makes it so much better
@DOCisChief The tension is quite obvious on that show. Had it on silent at a gym and I thought “boy they hate each other” just on body language lol

This analogy falls apart when you realize they couldn't have just moved on to or have been traded to another show (although HGTV could've definitely traded one of them to Fixer Upper or Property Brothers for a season). So since it falls apart, don't think about it.
